**Typography in tailwind**

1-Control font size, color, and angle.

1.
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-700">
  big text
</h1>
2.
<p class="text-sm italic text-gray-600">
Small and italic text
</p>

note:
text-{size} → (sm, md, lg, xl, 2xl…)
font-{weight} → (thin, normal, bold…)
italic → italic text
uppercase, lowercase, capitalize → Change case
